    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of various containers for shaking cocktails in order to mix ingredients; usually lidded, made of glass or metal, and of a tall shape designed to be conveniently held and shaken by hand.</Note_Text>
